**发现清单**

**F001**  
Severity: HIGH  
Category: code-bug  
Type: defect_fix  
Before-behavior: 流水线把模板区域语义 ID（如 `Q01`）直接当成 `StudentAnswer.question_id`，并把切图写到 `storage.root/<student_id>/<region_id>.png` 这种扁平路径下；一旦数据库拒绝该 `question_id`，错误还会被静默吞掉。  
After-behavior: 流水线应沿用现有扫描上传契约，按真实 `question_id`/`question_ids` 持久化，并使用按 `school/exam/subject/question/student` 隔离的存储路径；没有题目映射的模板不能伪装成“已成功入库”。  
Evidence: [pipeline_service.py](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/scan/pipeline_service.py#L102), [pipeline_service.py](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/scan/pipeline_service.py#L115), [pipeline_service.py](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/scan/pipeline_service.py#L118), [pipeline_service.py](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/scan/pipeline_service.py#L182), [pipeline_router.py](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/scan/pipeline_router.py#L99), [pipeline_router.py](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/scan/pipeline_router.py#L107), [pipeline_router.py](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/scan/pipeline_router.py#L110), [storage.py](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/shared/storage.py#L14), [storage.py](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/shared/storage.py#L21), [card/export.py](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/card/export.py#L64), [card/export.py](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/card/export.py#L95), [test_integration.py](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/tests/test_exam_misc/test_integration.py#L32), [test_integration.py](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/tests/test_exam_misc/test_integration.py#L142)  
Impact: 这会直接破坏扫描链路的核心契约。发布模板本来已经携带 `question_id`/`question_ids`，但流水线完全没用；实际结果要么是 `StudentAnswer` 因外键失败根本没落库，却仍被统计为 processed，要么即使落库也会因为扁平文件路径在跨考试/跨科目重复扫描时覆盖旧切图。AI 阅卷、人工阅卷、统计分析都会读不到正确答卷。  
Repair hypothesis: 可能的修复方向是先统一“模板区域 -> 真实 Question -> 存储路径”这条持久化契约，再决定 `.tpl` 来源模板在无题目映射时是补映射还是禁止进入持久化流程。禁止的修复模式：继续把 `Q01/OBJ01` 当 `question_id`；继续把所有 `IntegrityError` 一律当“重复数据”；继续使用 `storage.root/<student_id>/...` 的扁平输出目录。requires independent fix design + Semantic Regression Gate

